TracDjangoAuth
Trac Authentication against Django's userdb
(c) 2011 Ville Korhonen <ville@xd.fi>

Installation

 - NB: TracAccountManager plugin is REQUIRED
 - NB: Working Django installation is REQUIRED

 - pip install TracDjangoAuth
 - easy_install TracDjangoAuth
 - download TracDjangoAuth archive, unzip, python setup.py install OR python setup.py bdist_egg and copy dist/*.egg to plugins -directory inside your Trac environment
 
 
Edit trac.ini:
 [account-manager]
 password_store = DjangoPasswordStore
 require_group = Trac                   ; optional, in which Django group user must be to be authenticated